snippet.title: STAR BOY - Nigerian Movies 2025 Latest Full Movies
snippet.description:
STAR BOY follows Dekunle, a gifted young man from a humble background who dreams of lifting his family out of poverty. After losing job opportunities due to nepotism and being rejected by the woman he loves for not being “successful enough,” Dekunle finds hope through music. Encouraged by his loyal friend Sade, he enters a national singing competition that changes his life. As his fame rises, Dekunle must navigate fame, family secrets, and temptation — especially when his estranged brother Bayo resurfaces with ties to a dangerous criminal world. Amidst heartbreak, betrayal, and newfound purpose, Dekunle must choose between the fast life and the honest path to becoming the star he was born to be.

If you are searching for Nigerian Movies 2025 Latest Full Movies, don't miss STAR BOY! This gripping drama movie pulls you into the heart of Nollywood movies, latest movies, and everything fans love about new movie. A must-watch full movie and a powerful addition to the Omoni Oboli movies collection on Omoni Oboli Drama TV starring Clinton Joshua, Sophia Chisom (Soso), Daniel Rocky, Ayo Adesanya, Oma Obama.
